						<summary>

						<p>Records grant of 2 <hi rend="italic">mā</hi> of land by purchase by <hi rend="bold">Goppaṇaṉ,</hi> a <hi rend="italic">sēṉaibōga</hi> of <hi rend="bold">Valaya-Daṇḍanāyakar</hi> for providing flower garlands to the deity for his own merit. The land was made over to Periyakōyil-Nambi. The details of the date viz., <hi rend="bold">23rd year, Mīna, ba. 11, Pūśam, Sunday,</hi> are <hi rend="bold">irregular.</hi> </p>						

						</summary>
